Lesson 25 单词讲解

+ Mrs.          夫人
+ kitchen       厨房
+ refrigerator  电冰箱
+ fridge        冰箱
+ right         右边
+ left          左边
+ electric      带电的，可通电的
+ cooker        炉子，炊具
+ middle        中间
+ of            (属于)...的
+ room          房间
+ living room   客厅
+ dining room   餐厅
+ bedroom       卧室
+ bathroom      洗手间
+ cup           杯子



in the kitchen
on the right
The desk is on the right.
an electric cooker
an electric shaver
in the middle of

